        <num>40-493</num>
        <heading>Damages; costs; attorney fees</heading>
        <content>
          <p>In a civil action pursuant to section 40-492, the utility may recover as damages three times the amount of actual damages. The prevailing party shall recover reasonable attorney fees, costs and other expenses.</p>
